the anarchist teaching is that state should be abolished because it is immoral; that simple; but most people do not see immorality a bad thing when it is approved by a democratic majority, then they think it is wise violence; but they also can be convinced that some state activity is net negative, they just need practical arguments; when they get convinced then they will know not only that that particular activity by the state is net negative but will also recognize that something that is done by most states can be a mistake and then they will start questioning other activities too in a cascading way
